modName: Dovahkiin Imperial Logo for Layer Bikini
summary: Adds a Dovahkiin logo to Layer Bikini tops.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a Dovahkiin logo to all of Layer Bikini tops.  This mod requires you have installed http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7736 (Layer Bikini for UNP and CBBE by anano) and the mods required by that mod.

Extract, copy/cut and paste into the skyrim/Data/textures/Armor/LayerBikini folder.

Now everyone can see you\'re dragonborn.
author: FXtreme
